'''''Ben & Ara''''', ni Filime yikinamico ya Kameruni iyobowe na Nnegest Likké ayikorana na Joseph Baird, Constance Ejuma, Q'orianka Kilcher, Matthew Norsworthy na Samone Norsworthy for Nursing Tybalt Productions, Wonder Worthy Productions na N- vision production. Filime izenguruka  abakandida 2 ba PhD, umwe w’umuyisilamu wo muri [[Afurika]] undi agnostic, aho batangira gukundana nyuma yo guhurira mu nzu ndangamurage ariko nyuma bakavumbura ko urukundo hagati yimico itandukanye n’amadini rushobora kugira ingaruka.  

Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Joseph Baird na Constance Ejuma mu nshingano zabo, hamwe na Akuyoe Graham, Q'orianka Kilcher, Michael Chieffo na William Mark McCullough mu nshingano zabo.  Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi ndetse ikanerekanwa mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime.     Yerekanwe bwa mbere muri Nzeri 2015 mu iserukiramuco rya Filimi ryigenga rya Miami. Muri 2016, film yatsindiye ibihembo byamafoto meza n’umukinnyi mwiza mu iserukiramuco rya Filime Indie.  Umukinnyi w'amafirime nyamukuru Constance Ejuma yatsindiye igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Nevada.  Muri 2016, iyi filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Filime nziza ya Diaspora muri African Movie Academy Awards (AMAA). 

